Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆以言斷之神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡阻止的話  姐姐就不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從病房溜出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是  因為你看起來很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺也很精神呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家醫院的患者大部分都得了不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大概是昭和多少年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（昭和：日本天皇年號，元年1926年開始到1989年）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  到這裡之後都沒看過報紙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你是從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天町
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古森酒倉的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒倉？你家是釀酒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  您沒聽說過嗎  叫做古森的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這裡喝不到吧  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  沒關係  我以前很喜歡酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那是神賜予的聖水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了不是什麼好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天喝一點都會覺得難受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你還是孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為大人後就會覺得好喝了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得自己長大後必須繼承酒倉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我怎麼想的呢  大概吧  或許想過會繼承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母強迫你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  這倒沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你卻認為必須這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14歲  啊  滿15歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人生只有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說沒有過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟未來相比非常渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只有未來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有未來？那老爺爺你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經死去了  只是在這裡安詳的度過永久的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還有很多話想問  但我不能一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是突觸…我的腦內？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:59.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（突觸：synapse，也叫神經元連接點，兩個神經元間的功能連接結構，傳遞神經衝動）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…就是說這裡是比那邊更深的幽世？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這上面呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幽世待了多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺已經待了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然來到這裡就要繼續向前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能見到姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去看的話  一切都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去看就什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是怎樣的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那裡是死去的人去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡沒有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這種地方遇見你這麼「真實」的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真實」的人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:13:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  沒錯  在這裡感覺不需要保持人類的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？你又是誰！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見  這是一個抽象的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將這裡命名為「抽象界」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽象？那你是死去的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？我死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我的肉體好好活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在我耳邊說不去看就什麼都看不見的人  是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說不定真的是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你的形態好真實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初靈魂出竅時是兩頭身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後變得像古代的幽靈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後變成了跟現世一樣的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將這稱為靈魂出竅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將意識轉移到這個地方來  真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你那邊的說法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  信…啊  我的朋友是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信家是神社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能告訴我你的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？嗯…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Snark
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snark？Snark是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snark就是boojum
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就是指莫名其妙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你耍我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了吧？你是初中生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是高度抽象化的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你能久留的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我應該怎麼回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著想要回去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧姐他們還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們說發酵倉是不能進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣今年最後的麴菌就培育好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的做法都跟爺爺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長同意了試用我選的麴菌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（麴菌：把澱粉轉化為糖的菌）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能進來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有聲音傳出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  別這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的生命不斷誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起聯歡  真是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾者雖惡事一言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖善事一言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆以言斷之神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  還臥病在床嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼快就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙發燒在床上躺了一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂出竅時…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎  不行哦  居然去偷看女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有說服力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信  太郎說要去探望都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經上了多少台階？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對是魯莽的運動量或者要命的鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒退了  但她剛剛睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你們特地過來探病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒退了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都掉進河裡時我就在旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我馬上就把她從河裡拉上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把她背回這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事希望你早點告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  雖然她著涼的事我也很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但掉進河裡之前  都好像又被什麼附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像被什麼附身一樣  說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「吾者雖惡事一言  雖善事一言  皆以言斷之神」\N她這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都她真的這麼說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  請你們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這麼說話的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾者雖惡事一言…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個神社的女孩說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾者雖惡事一言  皆以言斷之神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像在哪聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老太婆叫你來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提倡獨特的基督教倫理學的Emanuel Swedenborg
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:40.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（Emanuel Swedenborg：瑞典科學家、哲學家和神秘主義者）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.71,0:24:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為靈魂的存在應該用物理方法探求
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.82,0:24:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而研究了腦生理學和解剖學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他體驗了幻覺  並能自由往來於死後的世界後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:24:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了這個研究
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:25:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來寫了純粹理性批判的Immanuel Kant\N也對Swedenborg的思想作出了很高的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:25:02.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（Immanuel Kant：1724-1804 德國哲學家、天文學家、星雲說的創立者之一，\N德國古典唯心主義創始人）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.96,0:25:04.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\an5\pos(640,495)}--突現基礎--
